1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:04,000
Every Dutch corporate must now report verified climate impact.

2
00:00:04,000 --> 00:00:08,000
Most of what they claim is unverifiable.
Greenwashing dressed up as compliance.

3
00:00:08,000 --> 00:00:13,000
Meanwhile, Dutch foodbanks rescue
40 million kilos of food a year.

4
00:00:13,000 --> 00:00:18,000
100,000 tCO2e avoided —
none of it on a single corporate report.

5
00:00:18,000 --> 00:00:23,000
Climate-Action Packages connect them.

6
00:00:23,000 --> 00:00:30,000
€25,000 buys 600 tonnes of CO2e
— methodology aligned with FRAME.

7
00:00:30,000 --> 00:00:36,000
One click. Solvimon takes the payment.

8
00:00:36,000 --> 00:00:45,000
Claude composes the audit-ready report —
every figure traceable, every source cited.

9
00:00:45,000 --> 00:00:50,000
12 foodbanks onboarded.
5 corporates committed.

10
00:00:50,000 --> 00:00:55,000
€425,000 of climate impact
bought before launch.

11
00:00:55,000 --> 00:01:00,000
Climate-Action Packages.
We make impact real.
